  "title": "Assistant Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<p>Create designs to entice consumers for the online retail market.</p>\n<p><strong>Primary duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Design banners and online collaterals</li>\n  <li>Create outstanding visuals for daily write-up</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>West area</li>\n  <li>Proficient in computer skills, especially an in-depth knowledge of Adobe Photoshop or Illustrator</li>\n  <li>Excellent spoken &amp; written communication skills in English and be able to bring forth his/her ideas succinctly.</li>\n  <li>Excellent interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Able to handle stress well and be comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Mature, confident, pro-active, organized and self-motivated</li>\n  <li>Excellent team player and ability to multi-task</li>\n  <li>Polytechnic diploma holders and candidates w/o experiences are welcomed to apply.</li>\n</ul>",
